# fluent-emojis/ must NOT be ignored: assets are vendored in-tree (not a live
# gitlink). Vite resolves /fluent-emoji/* → fluent-emojis/dist/* at build time
# (e.g. about-sharkey.vue → 1f3c6.png). Ignoring this path breaks `pnpm build`.
.pnp.*

